<header class="site-header size-lg text-center">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="col-xs-12">

      <h2>Hey, freelancer!<mark>GRAB</mark> your project!</h2>
      <h5 class="font-alt">Before someone else does.</h5>

    </div>

  </div>
</header>

<main>
  <section class="bg-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="section-header">
        <span>Latest</span>
        <h2>Recent jobs</h2>
        <p>Here's the last five job posted on the website</p>
      </header>

      <div class="row item-blocks-condensed">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
          <a class="item-block" href="job-detail.html">
            <header>
              <div class="hgroup">
                <h4>SOME TITLE</h4>
                <h5>SOME COMPNAY</h5>
              </div>
              <div class="header-meta">
                <span class="location">SOME LOCATION</span>
                <span class="label label-success">SOME FTE</span>
              </div>
            </header>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="section-header">
        <span>Reasons to join</span>
        <h2>Independancy</h2>
        <p>Some key features</p>
      </header>

      <div class="category-grid">

        <%= link_to about_path do %>
          <i class="fa fa-ban"></i>
          <h6>No recruiters</h6>
          <p>Third-party recruiters have been ruining the job market for far too long. They are not welcome here!</p>
        <% end %>

        <%= link_to about_path do %>
          <i class="fa fa-line-chart"></i>
          <h6>Earn more</h6>
          <p>Raise your income by going freelance. Not ready for freelancing? Try payrolling instead!</p>
        <% end %>

        <%= link_to about_path do %>
          <i class="fa fa-eye"></i>
          <h6>Transparent rates</h6>
          <p>Employers <strong>must</strong> show their pay rate. So you know what you are applying for.</p>
        <% end %>

      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">

      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
        <header class="section-header text-left">
          <span>More</span>
          <h2>Why SOME NAME?</h2>
        </header>

        <p class="lead">The sheer amount of recruiters is staggering. They often cost tons of money, but offer nothing that you cannot do yourself. So why use them? </p>
        <p>Most people have experienced it. Being spammed by recruiters with irrelevant job openings. Recruiters misspelling your name or not reading your resume.
        These recruiters cost alot of money - yet, they fail at the only thing they do. That's why we are better off without them.

        Face it, the employer will still be reviewing the resumes he receives. So why not just review relevant resumes and skip the recruiter all together? There's a huge
        financial opportunity for both employer and freelancer.
        </p>


        <br><br>
        <%= link_to 'Learn more', about_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
      </div>

      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 hidden-xs hidden-sm">
        <br>
        <img class="center-block" src="https://placeholdit.imgix.net/~text?txtsize=133&txt=1600%C3%97900&w=1600&h=900" alt="how it works">
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>


</main>
